          the local economy is on track to hit a $33 billion valuation, driven by high-value sectors like 
          health, tech, and clean energy.</li>
          <li><strong>Tight Supply:</strong> ABS Building Approvals remain below the levels required to meet 
          migration demand, keeping vacancy rates at record lows (sub-1%) and supporting sustained capital 
          growth.</li>
        </ul>

